  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for cups",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for cups fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2026-34980: Shared PostScript queue lets anonymous Print-Job requests reach `lp` code execution over the network (bsc#1261569).\n- CVE-2026-34990: Local print admin token disclosure using temporary printers (bsc#1261568).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
